This paper deals with the task of detecting suspicious news articles using micro blog text. The task involves natural language processing and information retrieval techniques, which are commonly studied in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Additionally, the paper also discusses the creation of a dataset and the use of machine learning techniques, which are relevant to the sub-categories of social and information networks (cs.SI), cyber security (cs.CY), and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
